{"tid":527094,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"笑到仆街鄰國真係出個home制比iPhone X","createTime":"2018-01-12T10:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T15:00:05.000Z","uid":1130,"like":358,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bc086a54ea440967535b57e79535cd0f561a80","tid":527094,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/01/12/iphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2Fiphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018%2F&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=460b4833\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/01/12/iphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/iphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018_00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fiphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018_00.png&h=783c58b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone X 沒了 Home 鍵，有些網民會嘲笑指蘋果會推出 Home 鍵配件代替，當然希望淘汰 Touch ID 的蘋果是不會這樣做，但是有中國配件商就為 iPhone X 用戶製作了「Home 鍵」。<br />\n<br />\n9to5Mac 網站總結在 CES 2018 蘋果產品配件的時候，他們介紹了這個 iPhone X 專用配件： Home 鍵，沒錯，這是為了 iPhone X 而設的 Home 鍵配件，插上 iPhone X，iPhone X 就可以重新擁有 Home 鍵，只是沒了 Touch ID 而已，除了 Home 鍵之外配件下方也有 3.5mm 接口，讓用戶可以一邊連接有線耳機聽歌，一邊連接 Lightning 線充電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/iphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fiphone-x-home-button-in-ces-2018_02.jpg&h=478457d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76c20b9e0febf190e45843132a6111261eb4b9d","tid":527